LogData.text: We’re finally making some progress. It could have been more, if Noémie didn’t stop us at every corner. She yells at us for doing nothing else but walking around. It’s not like we’re stupid, we know how to look left and right before entering a room. She doesn’t have to babysit us. She’s the one running into the actual dangerous places. I’ll have to get my med station ready, she’ll probably need it soon enough.
